quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,"Mi wonndirii Malaa'ikaaji sappiniraa…ói sappeejii, fii dewal majji."
  37,2,"Mi woondirii Mlaa'ikaaji soggiray…ói duule …óin, haa ka Alla muuyiri jipporde majje."
  37,3,"Mi woondirii Malaa'ikaaji janngooji daalol Alla …óin."
  37,4,"Pellet, rewetee…óo mon On, onon yim…ďe …ďen, e hoore goonga, ko bajjo, Mo alaa kafidii…óo: On woni Alla."
  37,5,"Jey…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, e kon ko woni hakkunde …óin …ói…ói, jey…óo kadi pu…óal e mutal naange ngen, hitaande nden fow."
  37,6,"Men labinirii kammu hikkii ngu aduna ngun, cu…óaari koode …óen, nannditayndi e kaŇčŇče jal…ďu…óe."
  37,7,"Men reeniri kammu hikkii ngu aduna ngun, koode …óen, fii da…óugol kala seytaane yatundu e …óoftaare Alla."
  37,8,"∆äin seytanooji ha…ótanaaka he…óitagol matu Malaa'ika ka kammu, tuma …ďe wowlata ko Joomi ma…ď…ďe wahayini e ma…ď…ďe, immorde e sari'aaji; tawde ontuma, hi…ói feroree baŇč-woo baŇč."
  37,9,"∆äum ko fii ra…óagol wata …ói he…óito Malaa'ika'en. E hoore …óum, hino woodani …ói kadi laakara, lepte muusu…óe, duumii…óe, …óe ta∆īondirtaa."
  37,10,"Si wanaa ndun seytaiiru biftii ndu e majji, jilannde haala, woni konngol e haala Malaa'ika'en, ko tawata fii mun hewtaali yim…ďe leydi …ďen; ontuma, ndu jokkintiniree hoodere hu…ď…ďunde, ko sunna ndu. Hino ara ka tawata ndu hewtinii ngol konngol jilaangol, e musidal mayru, haa ngol hewtoya ndaaroo…ďe …ďen, ado ndu fi…óireede hoodere sunnaynde nden, …ďe …ďeydita …óon, penaale teemedere."
  37,11,"An Muhammad, lamndo …ďee heefer…ďe yeddu…ďe fii ummital: si tawii ko kam…ďe …ďuri sa…ótude tagugol, e tii…óugol …ďalli, e mawnugol cemmbe, diini …ďen …ďe Men tagi ka kammuuli e ka leydi, wonndude e Malaa'ika'en? Men tagirii …ďe kam…ďe, loopal narnungal. Ko honno …ďe yeddirta fii ummital, e hoore ko e loopal lo'ungal narnungal …ďe tagiraa?"
  37,12,"Si ko woni, a haawi, an Muhammad, e kattal Alla ngal, e no O toppitora fiyakuuji tagu Makko ngun, haawi…óaa kadi, ko sirkoo…ďe …ďen yeddata kon fii ummital. Hakkee non ko …ďe sa…ótini fennugol fii maggal, hi…ďe jalnora ko wowlataa fii maggal."
  37,13,"Si …ďee sirkoo…ďe waajoraama kala noone e waaju, …ďe waajitortaa mo, sakko …ďe nafitora; hakkee ko …ďe yoori …ďer…óe."
  37,14,"Si …ďe yi'ii maande e maandeeji Annabiijo on (yo o his), tinndinde e goonga makko kan, …ďe fantina jalkitugol e haaweede."
  37,15,"∆Āe wi'a: Ko Muhammadu addi koo wonaali, si wanaa mbilewu …ďanngu ngu."
  37,16,"yoo si men maayii, men wontii mbullaari e ∆īi'e wu…óu…óe, haray men immintinoyte …ďaawo …óum? Waawaa wonnde."
  37,17,"Baabiraa…ďe amen, adinoo…ďe men kadi …ďen, immintinoyte …ďaawo maayde ma…ď…ďe?"
  37,18,"Maakan …ďe jaabo…óaa …ďe an Muhammad: Pellet, on immintinoyte …ďaawo nde on wontude mbullaari e ∆īi'e wo…óu…óe. Baabiraa…ďe mon adinoo…ďe …ďen kadi wano non. On fow on immintiniroyte jaasere e hoyneede."
  37,19,"Anndee …óum, ko wuttaandu wooturu pet ka alaandu (…ói…óa…ďuru ndun) tawaa jaka yoo, fow ma…ď…ďe hi…ďe ndaara kulaleeji √Ďalnde Darngal, hi…ďe habbitii ko Alla huuwata …ďe."
  37,20,"Sirkoo…ďe fennunoo…ďe ummital …ďen wi'oya ontuma: Ee halkaare amen ! Ko ndee woni √Ďalaande njo…ďdi kuu…óe …óen, nde Alla yo…ďitaya jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, golle …óe …ďe ardinnoo ka nguurndam ma…ď…ďe aduna."
  37,21,"∆Āe wi'anee ontuma: ko ndee tigiri, woni √Ďalaande √Īaawugol hakkunde jeyaa…ďe …ďen, nde √Ďalaande nde fennayno…óon fii mun aduna."
  37,22,"Malaa'ika'en wi'anee nden √Ďalnde: Moo…ďee sirkoo…ďe too√Īir…ďe sirku ma…ď…ďe on, e gartoo…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen ka sirkugol e ka fennugol, e …óin sanamuuji …ói …ďe rewaynoo …ďe acca Alla. ∆Āe holloya …ďe laawol Yiite ngol, …ďe soggiroya …ďe ton, tawde ko ton woni jaa∆īorde ma…ď…ďe."
  37,23,"37:22"
  37,24,"Darnon …ďe fii √Īaaweede, ado …ďe naadeede ka Yiite. ∆Āaawo …óum, soggiron …ďe ka Yiite."